    <content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Microsoft&amp;#8217;s &lt;a href="http://www.ironruby.net/"&gt;IronRuby&lt;/a&gt; is &lt;a href="http://rubyforge.org/pipermail/ironruby-core/2008-November/003250.html"&gt;moving to GitHub&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;div align="center"&gt;
&lt;a href="http://github.com/ironruby/ironruby"&gt;
&lt;img src="http://img.skitch.com/20081125-xugx44mr4yrqcgpxc3kw2nejew.png" alt="" /&gt;
&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

	&lt;p&gt;They&amp;#8217;ve already been here &lt;a href="http://github.com/ironruby"&gt;for a while&lt;/a&gt;, but now the main repository is officially moving.&lt;/p&gt;


	&lt;p&gt;IronRuby joins &lt;a href="http://github.com/evanphx/rubinius"&gt;Rubinius&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href="http://github.com/search?q=vm"&gt;dozens of other language implementations&lt;/a&gt;. Welcome, guys!&lt;/p&gt;</content>
